{"tid":235360,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[呂布]醫生驚嘆伊巴膝部超乎常人，邀作研究對象","createTime":"2017-05-09T03:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-09T06:39:45.000Z","uid":34571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f3e7f4a130ee51e6d915e2e52f9b643347e6714c","tid":235360,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:01:12.000Z","msg":"伊巴表示已完成了由傅浩強醫學教授主理的手術，很快就可再享受足球比賽。<br />\n<br />\n在診斷過程中，醫生發現伊巴膝部天生異稟，骨骼精奇，屬前所未見般強壯，因此希望日後能有機會以他作為研究個案。<br />\n<br />\n伊巴經理人拉奧拿向瑞典報章《Expressen》道出此事，他說：「醫生說他的膝部強壯得是他們前所未見的。他們認為他的膝蓋不可能是屬於踢了近二十年職業足球的人。」<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.newsamed.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/manchester-united-star-zlatan-ibrahimovics-road-to-recoveri-from-acl-injuri-has-not-convinced-jose-mourinho-he-has-a-future-at-club.jpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsamed.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2Fmanchester-united-star-zlatan-ibrahimovics-road-to-recoveri-from-acl-injuri-has-not-convinced-jose-mourinho-he-has-a-future-at-club.jpg.jpg&h=53bef36a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"85b2053e0a7e1cda525a63bacc973280b4b4470a","tid":235360,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:01:38.000Z","msg":"為伊巴治理的醫療團隊來自匹茲堡大學體育醫學中心，是專治膝部靭帶創傷的專家，見盡頂尖運動員的病例。<br />\n<br />\n「他們希望他在退役後能夠回來，讓他們對他的膝部和靭帶作出深入研究。」拉奧拿稱，伊巴答應了要求。<br />\n<br />\n年屆35歲的伊巴在季初以自由身加盟曼聯時，被不少人質疑以他的年紀未必可以應付英超比賽，但有傳他在進行體測時，打破了曼聯一些力量測試紀錄。他今季已於各項賽事取得28個入球，包括在社區盾和聯賽盃決賽的重要入球。<br />\n<br />\n除了是世界級足球員，伊巴也是一名習武三十年的跆拳道高手。<br />\n<br />\n在受傷前兩星期，伊巴曾形容自己是電影《奇幻逆緣》中的主角班傑明，年紀愈大，身體愈年輕。<img src=\"https://i.imgsafe.org/b36d35227c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgsafe.org%2Fb36d35227c.jpg&h=8d767928&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"09ccd3699c091c7f0bafb374386bdec05952d0b7","tid":235360,"uid":50328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:05:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e2f4f8292f68350d5f386fe6d5ef45bbd91374ad","tid":235360,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:06:55.000Z","msg":"再勁都會比摩連奴用殘"},{"pid":"0c2db37e4df907b0092fc3c6462a123c8722c8fd","tid":235360,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:19:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>再勁都會比摩連奴用殘</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ef880d78b729f9e9a523aeb74ed06c1f1dace0c","tid":235360,"uid":61201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:21:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e18429324967add437267d8e65e8376a434df6","tid":235360,"uid":68406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:40:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4b30a91a1c96876ad076e01c3bd8dfba772fdb","tid":235360,"uid":91763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T03:43:25.000Z","msg":"加度素都好似有類似體質, 好似話D骨勁到要特制手術刀先做到手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"726791608d8c12fa01fd73b693dd8c2e76c42664","tid":235360,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:02:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57eb0e5797d932ee9e8cabd58be42d5a6d6b7003","tid":235360,"uid":70013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-09T04:21:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>加度素都好似有類似體質, 好似話D骨勁到要特制手術刀先做到手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咪又係傷到要做手術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b76482f6f6cde177c087685b591137792f852b2b","tid":235